metadata.name: Stand for peace
metadata.description:
1/1  "Stand for peace"  AR (augmented reality) Soulmates NFT is created by AnnaStoko - a female Russian digital artist and software engineer. I'm here to spread the love, stand for peace and stop the war! 

Augmented Reality effects are available as a part of unlockable content. The .png format NFT will be sent after the purchase including the link to scan the NFT to see the full immersive effect. 

With love and faith in the bright future,
Anna
